{"tid":744492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[勇武]Pussy Riot闖世界盃決賽場　籲俄釋政治犯、停濫捕","createTime":"2018-07-16T03:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T00:42:24.000Z","uid":48124,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b6f0817b65e637b8d1014bbfc76261507a372842","tid":744492,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T03:33:07.000Z","msg":"數女子闖世盃決賽場　Pussy Riot 認責　籲俄釋政治犯、停濫捕<br />\n<br />\n立場報道2018/7/16 &mdash; 1:12<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法國大戰克羅地亞的世界盃決賽今晚在俄羅斯盧日尼基球場上演，在上半場發生一段插曲，在法國隊以2-1領先時，數名似是打扮成警察的人士 &mdash; 相信是女子 &mdash; 闖進了球場，但很快被保安人員帶走。一直敢於挑戰俄羅斯政治禁忌、批判威權統治的活躍團體 Pussy Riot 之後在社交媒體表示，闖入球場行動是她們的四名成員所為，Pussy Riot 批評俄羅斯警察無法無天，要求俄羅斯釋放所有政治犯、停止非法逮捕集會人士、容許政治競爭、停止無根據的檢控和冤獄等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%95%B8%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E9%97%96%E4%B8%96%E7%9B%83%E6%B1%BA%E8%B3%BD%E5%A0%B4-pussy-riot-%E8%AA%8D%E8%B2%AC-%E7%B1%B2%E4%BF%84%E9%87%8B%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E7%8A%AF-%E5%81%9C%E6%BF%AB%E6%8D%95/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E9%2597%2596%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%259B%2583%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E5%25A0%25B4-pussy-riot-%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25B2%25AC-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E4%25BF%2584%25E9%2587%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E7%258A%25AF-%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25BF%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%2F&d=YANgR46M55LsrvAyiDZ4Jtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=39456427\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E9%2597%2596%25E4%25B8%2596%25E7%259B%2583%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E8%25B3%25BD%25E5%25A0%25B4-pussy-riot-%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25B2%25AC-%25E7%25B1%25B2%25E4%25BF%2584%25E9%2587%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E7%258A%25AF-%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25BF%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%2F&h=e39bae9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%95%B8%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E9%97%96%E4%B8%96%E7%9B%83%E6%B1%BA%E8%B3%BD%E5%A0%B4-pussy-riot-%E8%AA%8D%E8%B2%AC-%E7%B1%B2%E4%BF%84%E9%87%8B%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E7%8A%AF-%E5%81%9C%E6%BF%AB%E6%8D%95/</a>"},{"pid":"ed065f3deb70480ee381291ada4717c007df990d","tid":744492,"uid":82350,"like":7,"dislike":24,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T04:56:59.000Z","msg":"有克羅地亞球員出泥屌鬼<br />\n<br />\n打Cupfinal心情我明<br />\n<br />\n但唔該諗番下<br />\n當年克羅地亞人民到成個巴爾車幹以至整個東歐<br />\n<br />\n就係比蘇共<br />\n呢d人類歷史垃圾死全家屌老母大渣再<br />\n<br />\n害到雞毛鴨血手<br />\n<br />\n對住強權暴政<br />\n<br />\n有人走出泥屌佢老母<br />\n係為左公義<br />\n<br />\n靜落泥<br />\n格仔球應該反省下"},{"pid":"ec0c17ab6c9ebe5402b24db5089d83806a963ff5","tid":744492,"uid":60658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ed065f3deb70480ee381291ada4717c007df990d","tid":744492,"uid":82350,"like":7,"dislike":24,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T04:56:59.000Z","msg":"有克羅地亞球員出泥屌鬼<br />\n<br />\n打Cupfinal心情我明<br />\n<br />\n但唔該諗番下<br />\n當年克羅地亞人民到成個巴爾車幹以至整個東歐<br />\n<br />\n就係比蘇共<br />\n呢d人類歷史垃圾死全家屌老母大渣再<br />\n<br />\n害到雞毛鴨血手<br />\n<br />\n對住強權暴政<br />\n<br />\n有人走出泥屌佢老母<br />\n係為左公義<br />\n<br />\n靜落泥<br />\n格仔球應該反省下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T04:59:05.000Z","msg":"識唔識字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"482c1ed0967a1d35771280470441484dbc8e35bb","tid":744492,"uid":53524,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T05:05:43.000Z","msg":"死垃圾俄狗<br />\n抗議到要坑克羅地亞一鑊"},{"pid":"fee274fe62c47dea27784b40c637f18b563608db","tid":744492,"uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:06:30.000Z","msg":"事件發生於下半場約10分鐘，克羅地亞落後2比1並準備反撃期間，4名身穿警察服裝的示威者突然衝入球場，克羅地亞後衛洛夫雲（Dejan Lovren）嘗試攔截示威者不果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，其中一名示威者更與法國前鋒麥巴比（Kylian Mbapp&eacute;）擊掌，最終所有示威者被保安制伏帶走。<br />\n<br />\nPussy Riot隨後於Facebook及Twitter發表聲明，內容主要包括要求俄羅斯政府釋放所有政治犯、禁止在集會非法拘捕示威人士及政治迫害、引入政治競爭等。該樂隊其中一名隊員Olga Kurachyova接受路透社電話訪問，表示自己已經被捕。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯總統普京（Vladimir Putin）是決賽的座上客，大會並沒有在示威期間捕捉到他的表情，亦未知他會否對示威作回應。"},{"pid":"e5ed6ead71afcd8a4e01eb507756db1d0d5ca149","tid":744492,"uid":143572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:13:18.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆, 佢地示威完都冇乜人知佢地想表達乜。<br />\n大部份唔睇新聞既以為佢地落場出風頭既ON9 fans。<br />\n傳媒都特別去講。"},{"pid":"ec8c866f85dcee422e5e2dc7cf1c8f1322988c48","tid":744492,"uid":36880,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:18:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea5b9d82d2e8f8e09f854b0941ae33fe243505e9","tid":744492,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:24:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持"},{"pid":"07b1a8a2cc2f8ab7f89e50269dc2853cc52c0c44","tid":744492,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"482c1ed0967a1d35771280470441484dbc8e35bb","tid":744492,"uid":53524,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T05:05:43.000Z","msg":"死垃圾俄狗<br />\n抗議到要坑克羅地亞一鑊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:25:08.000Z","msg":"坑乜春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee54db001131a886f0d2a92244f655a8c233c4d6","tid":744492,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec8c866f85dcee422e5e2dc7cf1c8f1322988c48","tid":744492,"uid":36880,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"482c1ed0967a1d35771280470441484dbc8e35bb","tid":744492,"uid":53524,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T05:05:43.000Z","msg":"死垃圾俄狗<br />\n抗議到要坑克羅地亞一鑊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:18:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:31:02.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"64b862b59e5a59f3b342414a1448bcb77ee41ca2","tid":744492,"uid":86898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:35:03.000Z","msg":"咁都叫勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同遊行完唱歌有咩分別"},{"pid":"ef518604f29da3c8154f3399ae6e1d5b0b2cdbe9",